<p><rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">block</rs> incorporating a simple moulding, (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.02</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.48</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.33</measure>). Part of a composite monument; the probable restoration of l. 2 strongly suggests that a block of equal size constituted the missing right half of the monument.</p>
</div>

